    "created_at": "2016-02-25T05:34:39Z",
    "updated_at": "2016-02-25T05:35:11Z",
    "body": "> if you leave notifications in the center, users will be annoyed with you and claim that you should remove them.\n\nGoing out on a limb here, but what they _probably_ mean is that the notifications should go away when you return to the app and see what they were pointing to (which is obviously the application's problem, not Electron's). Notifications that persist after their usefulness are just as annoying as notifications that don't persist long enough.\n"
